<bibRefCitation id="EFDBA4A8FFA43C5EFEA3B9E8FDB883C3" author="Bournier" box="[351,558,1980,2005]" firstAuthor="Bournier" page="363" pageId="2" pageNumber="240" pagination="357 - 366" refId="ref3162" refString="Bournier, A. (1993) Thysanopteres gallicoles de Nouvelle-Caledonie. Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 98, 357 - 366. https: // doi. org / 10.3406 / bsef. 1993.17908" type="journal article" year="1993">Bournier, 1993: 363</bibRefCitation>
